summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department, authorizing negotiation for and acquisition of easements required for the construction of the Southwest Kenyon Street Sanitary Sewer Project, across certain property in Blocks 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 12, 13, 15, 16, 17, 18, 20, 21 and 36 in State Addition No. 4, Block 1, Rahn's Addition, Block 3, Dumar's Highland Park, Supplemental Plat, the SE 1/4 of Section 30, and the SE 1/4 and the NE 1/4 of the SW 1/4 of Section 31, Township 24 North, Range 4 East W.M., and making an appropriation from the Municipal Sewerage 1971 Construction Fund therefor.
